Streamlit Deployed Dashboard: https://ai-talent-engine-zw9jdtdpgzu4thfjdig7qe.streamlit.app

How to run codes?
Data is currently being accessed from Hugging Face (50K rows too big for GitHub)

1. Get Raw data using ingestion.py (ensure people data labs API is being used for this) - add your own key
 - Alternative to using API: create synthetic data using create_data.py
 - Uncomment the respective portion being used from ingestion.py

2. Run scoring.py for creating scores and tiers (and more)
 - The creation logics have been added to the code

3. Run UI.py to deploy the dashboard on Streamlit

4. All above codes can be run directly using main.py (this is the final production-level code)
